\subtree{
\title{Success Criteria}
\p{A complete CodeQL analysis run should satisfy:}

\ul{
\li{[ ] Output directory resolved (user-specified or auto-incremented default)}
\li{[ ] All generated files stored inside \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR\stopverb}}
\li{[ ] Database built (discovered via \code{\startverb codeql-database.yml\stopverb} marker) with quality assessment passed (baseline LoC > 0, errors < 5\%)}
\li{[ ] Data extensions evaluated — either created in \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/extensions/\stopverb} or explicitly skipped with justification}
\li{[ ] Analysis run with explicit suite reference (not default pack suite)}
\li{[ ] All installed query packs (official + Trail of Bits + Community) used or explicitly excluded}
\li{[ ] Selected query packs logged to \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/rulesets.txt\stopverb}}
\li{[ ] Unfiltered results preserved in \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/raw/results.sarif\stopverb}}
\li{[ ] Final results in \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/results/results.sarif\stopverb} (filtered for important-only, copied for run-all)}
\li{[ ] Zero-finding results investigated (database quality, model coverage, suite selection)}
\li{[ ] Build log preserved at \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/build.log\stopverb} with all commands, fixes, and quality assessments}
}
}
}